An '''Al'ma'den''' was one of the popal [[Priest/Legends|priests]] in the [[Ni'Shaw-Dak Ministry|Ni'Shaw-Dak]] religion. A high rank, the Al'ma'dens were only second to the [[Third Prophet]]. There were only twelve Al'ma'den in the religion, housed at the Ministry headquarters.<ref name="AIR">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

